\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The framework was compared to a heterogeneous robot fleet that just randomly explored with D* Lite.
 The graph shows twenty iterations of both algorithm's performance based on how many timesteps were needed to explore the entire map and how much battery life remaining at the end of the simulation.
